    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158530/extras/85bc6a2264a6fbf973455c94e5b06001.avif?t=1713175022\" width=600 height=190 /></span><br><br>空中平台是第一人称平台游戏，您可以在一定时间内完成关卡, <br>运用敏捷性和技巧在不同的物体上跳跃，躲避障碍物 &quot;地板是熔岩quot;游戏类型。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158530/extras/046722f56292d55bd734ee517bdd7474.poster.avif?t=1713175022\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158530/extras/046722f56292d55bd734ee517bdd7474.webm?t=1713175022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158530/extras/046722f56292d55bd734ee517bdd7474.mp4?t=1713175022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当旋转物体、激光、落石、爆炸和更多危险增加时，你走得越远，游戏就会变得越困难和更具挑战性。最重要的是，每个级别都有一个计时器，其中包含完成该级别所需的时间<br><br><strong>特征:</strong><br><br><strong>•</strong>关卡越来越疯狂的战役<br><br><strong>•</strong>当你达到更高的水平时解锁新技能<br><br><strong>•</strong>具有高分系统的计时赛级别的单独模式<br><br>进入计时赛模式，选择一个级别并尽快完成它，取得更好的成绩。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158530/extras/f677b668ef2f1da7c91b10aee1bbeee2.poster.avif?t=1713175022\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158530/extras/f677b668ef2f1da7c91b10aee1bbeee2.webm?t=1713175022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158530/extras/f677b668ef2f1da7c91b10aee1bbeee2.mp4?t=1713175022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>*</strong> <strong>附加信息</strong><br><br>■ 当您第一次打开战役时，您将有总共 50 个级别来完成游戏。总共5个世界。<br><br>■ 一开始没有解锁的能力。第一个能力技能从11级开始解锁。<br><br>■ 计时赛模式已开放，但你不会拥有技能，除非你在战役中解锁了它们。",
